      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "EARS THE BOSS (5) finished eighth last start over 2240m at Swan Hill, beaten 90 metres, after a good second at Cranbourne the run prior. Finds a suitable assignment and can bounce straight back. BEARTASTIC WRITER (1) drew a wide gate last start and was never a genuine threat, beaten 13 metres into seventh at this track over 2190m. Meets a similar line up and from a far better starting position he can figure in the finish. ROJENBYE (10) was in the money two starts ago then things went amiss last start when he copped a check, broke, and finished 11 metres away in fifth over 2190m at this track. Will need an ounce of luck to slot in from this tricky draw. Beautifully placed and is able to make amends. PUNTO CALIENTE (4) is in the mix following a fifth at his first run back over 2190m at this track.",
